gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 114, Spurs 105
gameRecap.excerpt: Minnesota defeats San Antonio, 114-105. For Minnesota, Anthony Edwards recorded 34 points, five rebounds, and five assists aided by Naz Reid adding 22 points and six rebounds to lead the way in the victory. Devin Vassell led the way for the Spurs with 21 points, six rebounds, and six assists while Keldon Johnson tallied 20 points, six rebounds, and four assists and Victor Wembanyama added 17 points, 13 rebounds, five assists, and four blocks for San Antonio in the losing effort. Minnesota wins and improves to 41-17 on the season, while San Antonio moves to 11-48 with the loss.
